1
00:01:01,429 --> 00:01:03,030
Well, then shall we...

2
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:06,040
start talking?

3
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:10,140
You two have been just
staring at each other.

4
00:01:11,439 --> 00:01:12,540
Well...

5
00:01:13,650 --> 00:01:17,450
Will you say I have a grudge again
now that I don't speak?

6
00:01:20,290 --> 00:01:21,650
Did I upset you?

7
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:26,120
Did you hold grudges again?

8
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:30,599
I don't talk...

9
00:01:31,859 --> 00:01:33,060
because I'm considerate.

10
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:36,170
Do you get it?

11
00:01:36,569 --> 00:01:38,340
It's because I'm considerate.

12
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,370
Do you know
what being considerate means?

13
00:01:41,109 --> 00:01:43,480
I try to understand others that they
might have...

14
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:46,739
their own reasons and
they might stop someday.

15
00:01:47,810 --> 00:01:51,879
I endured and waited.

16
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:55,519
Then I went through a lot...

17
00:01:56,019 --> 00:01:58,459
to start talking like this.

18
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:01,290
I want you to know that.

19
00:02:03,659 --> 00:02:04,659
Hwan Gi!

20
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:08,270
Do you think I say
all I want to say?

21
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,199
- I think you do.
- No.

22
00:02:10,270 --> 00:02:11,770
- No?
- No!

23
00:02:12,069 --> 00:02:13,939
Gosh. I doubt it.

24
00:02:13,969 --> 00:02:16,610
I talk more than you just because...

25
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,840
I have much to say.

26
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:23,009
I barely get to say
what I really want to say.

27
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,280
I hesitate too.

28
00:02:27,219 --> 00:02:29,150
I also think carefully...

29
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:31,520
and hold back. Do you know that?

30
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,430
No, you don't.

31
00:02:35,689 --> 00:02:38,400
You think and hold back?

32
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:42,569
I can understand both of you.

33
00:02:43,169 --> 00:02:45,900
Shall we start talking about
what you really want to say?

34
00:02:45,939 --> 00:02:47,870
- Let me start first.
- Hey.

35
00:02:48,139 --> 00:02:51,840
Wait. How dare you start first?

36
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,849
Where is my alcohol?

37
00:02:54,979 --> 00:02:57,580
My alcohol is gone. Where is it?

38
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:05,020
- We need more drinks now.
- I'll go get it.

39
00:03:05,090 --> 00:03:07,590
- I'm okay.
- I'll bring some more.

40
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:10,430
You just stay here.
You better not run away.

41
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:15,699
There you go!

42
00:03:16,169 --> 00:03:18,740
I won!

43
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,039
We are here.

44
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:25,409
We are almost there.
Please move a bit more.

45
00:03:26,139 --> 00:03:28,180
- Shall we go?
- No.

46
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:30,280
I'm too tired.

47
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:34,250
There, there.

48
00:03:35,050 --> 00:03:36,990
- Please untie this.
- Do you want to untie that?

49
00:03:37,090 --> 00:03:38,159
Are you stuffy?

50
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,590
- Yes, I am.
- Okay.

51
00:03:40,889 --> 00:03:42,860
It's done now.

52
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:44,599
- Thanks.
- No problem.

53
00:03:49,729 --> 00:03:50,740
Gosh...

54
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:54,039
I have one more to carry.

55
00:03:57,340 --> 00:03:58,780
Are you crying?

56
00:04:09,449 --> 00:04:11,590
She's so ugly.

57
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:20,529
- Oh, my goodness.
- I do look so ugly.

58
00:04:20,629 --> 00:04:22,730
That totally sobered me up.

59
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:27,439
I won.

60
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:32,439
I'm injured, but I still won.

61
00:04:35,810 --> 00:04:37,480
Does it still hurt?

62
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:52,230
Your photo was...

63
00:04:52,329 --> 00:04:53,459
so funny.

64
00:04:54,069 --> 00:04:55,699
Go on. Laugh as you want!

65
00:04:56,329 --> 00:04:58,339
You didn't laugh
when I wanted you to do so.

66
00:05:04,910 --> 00:05:06,040
We're here.

67
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:13,019
Oh, boy.

68
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,319
Almost there.

69
00:06:05,670 --> 00:06:08,069
She's so ugly.

70
00:06:19,579 --> 00:06:23,220
I didn't know he could laugh
so much like this.

71
00:06:28,329 --> 00:06:29,959
He looks beautiful.

72
00:06:34,670 --> 00:06:41,569
(Episode 9, If You Listen)

73
00:06:44,709 --> 00:06:46,480
Where did Ro Woon go?

74
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:49,009
She promised to go on
a tour together.

75
00:06:50,519 --> 00:06:51,519
Ro Woon!

76
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:55,490
Ro Woon! Ro Woon!

77
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:14,069
Move your leg away.

78
00:07:14,139 --> 00:07:15,910
I am sorry.

79
00:07:19,709 --> 00:07:22,379
Move your head.
You're using my arm as pillow.

80
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,519
- I'm not.
- You are.

81
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:27,149
I said to move your leg. It's heavy.

82
00:07:27,189 --> 00:07:28,449
I did it.

83
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:30,889
Whose leg is this then?

84
00:07:33,089 --> 00:07:34,759
Get off me. Seriously.

85
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:38,160
What are you talking about?

86
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,949
- Put her head away.
- What?

87
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:02,519
Do it gently.

88
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,759
Hurry up!

89
00:08:28,980 --> 00:08:30,110
Gosh.

90
00:08:42,259 --> 00:08:43,429
Do you want some coffee?

91
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:50,070
She's so odd.

92
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:54,009
With her, we might be able to go
back to how things were before.

93
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:57,440
Thanks to her,

94
00:08:57,840 --> 00:09:00,750
we fought, argued,

95
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:02,250
and laughed just like in the past.

96
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,919
I want things to be like that
in the future as well.

97
00:09:09,850 --> 00:09:10,889
For that to happen,

98
00:09:12,659 --> 00:09:13,820
I'd better not...

99
00:09:15,230 --> 00:09:16,730
marry Yi Soo.

100
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:20,529
I say this to you honestly...

101
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:24,440
because I don't want to lose you.

102
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:28,240
It could be my greed,
but I hope you understand me.

103
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,740
You've never brought out...

104
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:36,509
what happened
three years ago, right?

105
00:09:57,100 --> 00:09:59,669
How can someone like me...

106
00:10:01,570 --> 00:10:03,240
How can I...

107
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:07,210
I think I made...

108
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:13,080
a terrible mistake that
I should've never made.

109
00:10:14,250 --> 00:10:15,750
Please don't say that.

110
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:32,500
I feel too guilty for her
to stay with Yi Soo.

111
00:10:34,669 --> 00:10:36,570
It's also not right...

112
00:10:37,210 --> 00:10:38,809
to stay with her feeling like this.

113
00:10:40,409 --> 00:10:42,549
I realized only after
sending her like that.

114
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:46,019
The biggest mistake I made was...

115
00:10:46,879 --> 00:10:48,789
not choosing her.

116
00:10:50,220 --> 00:10:51,590
I don't want to...

117
00:10:52,690 --> 00:10:54,090
repeat the same mistake.

118
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:57,460
I'm not going to repeat
the same mistake either.

119
00:10:59,330 --> 00:11:00,899
I'm not going to hesitate anymore.

120
00:11:02,669 --> 00:11:04,039
What do you mean?

121
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,039
The one you're about to choose is...

122
00:11:10,539 --> 00:11:12,179
Ms. Chae's little sister.

123
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:15,309
- What?
- Chae Ro Woon is...

124
00:11:16,809 --> 00:11:18,919
Chae Ji Hye's little sister.
Do you understand?

125
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:21,750
What are you talking about?

126
00:11:25,789 --> 00:11:26,960
Are you sure?

127
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,429
Why didn't you tell me?

128
00:11:32,529 --> 00:11:34,100
I told you to fire her.

129
00:11:34,700 --> 00:11:36,269
Were you aware of it
from the beginning?

130
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,799
Why didn't you...

131
00:11:40,539 --> 00:11:41,710
Wait.

132
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:47,580
Why did Ro Woon enter
our company in the first place?

133
00:11:49,009 --> 00:11:50,279
Leave her...

134
00:11:51,279 --> 00:11:52,519
be.

135
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:53,879
What?

136
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:57,350
- Don't do anything to her.
- What are you...

137
00:11:57,389 --> 00:11:58,659
I can't...

138
00:12:02,529 --> 00:12:03,860
let her go now.

139
00:13:09,490 --> 00:13:11,100
Why are you coming out of
Boss's room?

140
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:12,500
What?

141
00:13:12,799 --> 00:13:15,169
It's not like that.
I just came to look for him.

142
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:18,100
That's not true. I saw you
coming out of there.

143
00:13:18,299 --> 00:13:19,440
No.

144
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:22,309
It's not like that.
I'm just looking for him.

145
00:13:23,370 --> 00:13:24,639
Why this early in the morning?

146
00:13:26,179 --> 00:13:27,480
Breakfast.

147
00:13:28,309 --> 00:13:29,580
He should have breakfast.

148
00:13:31,250 --> 00:13:34,049
Just to say that
he should have breakfast,

149
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:36,450
you hurried here
as soon as you woke up?

150
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,019
You haven't even washed your face.

151
00:13:40,389 --> 00:13:41,830
Your hair is a mess.

152
00:13:41,990 --> 00:13:43,590
Stop it.

153
00:13:48,029 --> 00:13:50,799
Gyo Ri, you're sharing a room
with Ro Woon, right?

154
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,399
Hey.

155
00:13:52,570 --> 00:13:55,340
- I was wondering if you slept well.
- Gyo Ri.

156
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:57,509
- Gyo Ri.
- Where are you now?

157
00:13:58,509 --> 00:14:01,250
- Okay, I'll be right there.
- Hey.

158
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,809
- Okay.
- Wait.

159
00:14:03,879 --> 00:14:05,519
Hey, stop.

160
00:14:08,019 --> 00:14:09,190
Wait.

161
00:14:11,889 --> 00:14:15,429
I can't understand a word
of what you're saying.

162
00:14:15,789 --> 00:14:17,289
She's here to take revenge.

163
00:14:18,429 --> 00:14:20,429
She's the one who published
the article on my power abuse.

164
00:14:20,460 --> 00:14:21,730
Is that true?

165
00:14:23,429 --> 00:14:24,639
Why did you...

166
00:14:25,470 --> 00:14:28,509
- keep it to yourself?
- I thought she could get hurt.

167
00:14:28,539 --> 00:14:29,769
That's why I didn't tell you.

168
00:14:29,809 --> 00:14:33,639
- If Father finds out...
- So let's keep it from him.

169
00:14:34,139 --> 00:14:35,549
Don't say anything to Ro Woon.

170
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:37,679
She doesn't know
that I'm aware of it.

171
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:46,159
Se Jong, let me explain, okay?

172
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:48,460
- Come here.
- It hurts.

173
00:14:48,490 --> 00:14:50,730
Se Jong.

174
00:14:51,230 --> 00:14:53,929
I'm getting even more suspicious
because you're stopping me.

175
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:56,870
There's nothing to be suspicious of.
What are you talking about?

176
00:14:56,899 --> 00:14:59,600
- Is that so?
- Wait.

177
00:15:01,769 --> 00:15:03,110
Stop!

178
00:15:03,210 --> 00:15:06,409
Why are you so fast? Hey!

179
00:15:06,980 --> 00:15:08,210
Stop right there!

180
00:15:08,549 --> 00:15:09,779
I want to...

181
00:15:12,279 --> 00:15:14,389
protect her this time.

182
00:15:16,919 --> 00:15:19,159
If you're feeling guilty
about what happened to Ms. Chae,

183
00:15:20,690 --> 00:15:22,360
protect her by all means.

184
00:15:39,379 --> 00:15:41,980
Very good. Let's do a cat pose now.

185
00:15:43,309 --> 00:15:46,750
Come down. Breathe.

186
00:15:47,789 --> 00:15:49,250
Breathe out.

187
00:15:51,190 --> 00:15:52,860
And come back up.

188
00:15:53,519 --> 00:15:54,730
That'd be it.

189
00:15:55,830 --> 00:15:59,500
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

190
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:04,230
Gyo Ri.

191
00:16:07,299 --> 00:16:09,740
Ro Woon didn't come to the room
last night, did she?

192
00:16:11,509 --> 00:16:12,740
I don't know.

193
00:16:13,379 --> 00:16:17,509
- I went to bed early last night.
- You would have noticed her.

194
00:16:17,750 --> 00:16:20,419
She snores so loud.

195
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:29,590
Gyo Ri.

196
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:33,259
- Hey.
- Tell me the truth.

197
00:16:33,929 --> 00:16:35,330
Who did you sleep with last night?

198
00:16:35,769 --> 00:16:37,970
Boss? Mr. Kang?

199
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:39,840
Or both?

200
00:16:40,539 --> 00:16:41,940
You're amazing.

201
00:16:42,809 --> 00:16:44,980
That's right. I slept with him.

202
00:16:45,009 --> 00:16:46,710
I slept with Boss.
Are you happy now?

203
00:16:48,179 --> 00:16:49,309
See?

204
00:16:49,879 --> 00:16:51,379
You like Boss.

205
00:16:53,519 --> 00:16:55,289
We just slept.

206
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:58,720
He got drunk,
so I took him to his room.

207
00:16:59,289 --> 00:17:01,629
And then I fell asleep.

208
00:17:02,090 --> 00:17:03,759
Do you expect me to believe that?

209
00:17:05,730 --> 00:17:09,400
Fine, don't believe it.
That's great.

210
00:17:09,529 --> 00:17:12,670
Now, you could finally stop
harassing me.

211
00:17:12,839 --> 00:17:16,069
Do you think
I'm trying to harass you?

212
00:17:16,109 --> 00:17:18,910
You keep crossing the line
making others uncomfortable.

213
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,180
You're just fooling around with me.

214
00:17:23,210 --> 00:17:24,480
I'm fooling around with you?

215
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:27,279
I looked for you everywhere
all night.

216
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,720
I wanted to show you fireflies.

217
00:17:29,890 --> 00:17:32,089
I stayed up all night
waiting for you.

218
00:17:32,819 --> 00:17:34,460
Do you still think
I'm fooling around with you?

219
00:17:39,599 --> 00:17:41,529
Se Jong.

220
00:18:02,019 --> 00:18:03,450
Boss.

221
00:18:04,089 --> 00:18:06,619
- Where's Mr. Kang?
- He went back.

222
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:09,859
Did something come up?

223
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,730
I'm sorry.

224
00:18:17,970 --> 00:18:20,900
I fell asleep in your bed.

225
00:18:24,369 --> 00:18:26,509
In addition, I got caught.

226
00:18:26,539 --> 00:18:30,309
By Se Jong, the big mouth.

227
00:18:31,349 --> 00:18:33,519
I should have kept my mouth shut,

228
00:18:33,619 --> 00:18:35,720
but he was so persistent.

229
00:18:36,450 --> 00:18:37,650
Also...

230
00:18:41,230 --> 00:18:42,759
I'm not supposed to tell anyone,

231
00:18:44,829 --> 00:18:46,900
but you're good at keeping secrets.

232
00:18:47,559 --> 00:18:49,130
It's only between you and me.

233
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,369
The thing is,

234
00:18:54,710 --> 00:18:57,269
Gyo Ri has a crush on Se Jong.

235
00:18:57,910 --> 00:19:00,839
I thought it might help Se Jong
give up on me.

236
00:19:00,940 --> 00:19:03,150
He says he likes me all the time.

237
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:05,319
I feel so sorry for Gyo Ri.

238
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:11,289
You laughed so much last night.

239
00:19:12,819 --> 00:19:16,029
You turned into an adolescent boy
overnight.

240
00:19:18,799 --> 00:19:22,170
I have no idea
what's going through your mind.

241
00:19:24,269 --> 00:19:25,640
Speaking of which,

242
00:19:26,539 --> 00:19:29,869
I've been thinking about
how to communicate with you.

243
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:35,910
What is this?

244
00:19:35,950 --> 00:19:37,609
Stay still.

245
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:39,319
Ta-da.

246
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:42,920
There you go.

247
00:19:45,519 --> 00:19:48,029
- It's a signal light.
- Sorry?

248
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:52,130
You communicate your mood
using different colors.

249
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:54,460
When you don't want to be
bothered by anyone,

250
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,970
turn on the red light.

251
00:19:57,730 --> 00:20:00,440
When you're available for urgent
matters, turn on the yellow light.

252
00:20:01,039 --> 00:20:05,079
When you're feeling ready for
all kinds of discussion,

253
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:07,910
turn on the green light.

254
00:20:09,509 --> 00:20:11,880
This is too... I'm okay.

255
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:15,650
You might feel awkward at first,

256
00:20:15,990 --> 00:20:18,190
but you'll get used to it
eventually.

257
00:20:20,359 --> 00:20:21,460
Here.

258
00:20:22,759 --> 00:20:25,430
Right now, it's the red light.

259
00:20:26,660 --> 00:20:27,759
Isn't it?

260
00:20:31,170 --> 00:20:33,200
I'll stop talking.

261
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:36,009
Just relax.

262
00:20:47,849 --> 00:20:49,450
How can she say such a thing?

263
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:51,920
How dare she belittle me like that?

264
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:09,009
I'm not fooling around with her...

265
00:21:16,410 --> 00:21:18,180
I wanted to look cool
in front of Ro Woon,

266
00:21:18,380 --> 00:21:21,019
so I even got these limited-edition
sneakers yesterday.

267
00:21:28,789 --> 00:21:32,200
Right. She might think
that I'm too stylish for her.

268
00:21:32,299 --> 00:21:33,599
Yes, that must be it.

269
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:35,829
It's all because of my good looks.

270
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:38,500
That's why she can't see how sincere
I am and doesn't take me seriously.

271
00:21:40,269 --> 00:21:41,740
