272
00:21:45,109 --> 00:21:48,180
That was the reason!
My good looks were to blame!

273
00:21:49,980 --> 00:21:53,480
My sneakers! Oh, no. My sneakers...

274
00:21:54,789 --> 00:21:55,849
What is he doing?

275
00:21:57,220 --> 00:21:59,089
Is he being like that
because of Ro Woon?

276
00:22:00,019 --> 00:22:01,059
Se Jong!

277
00:22:02,029 --> 00:22:03,029
Se Jong!

278
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:06,130
Oh, no. My sneakers...

279
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,930
- Se Jong!
- Let go.

280
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,500
