or something.

289
00:22:38,759 --> 00:22:40,359
Why would I hate you?

290
00:22:41,299 --> 00:22:43,869
You've been distant
ever since you found out...

291
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:45,640
who my grandfather is.

292
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:48,109
Well, that's...

293
00:22:48,170 --> 00:22:50,569
It's okay. That's normal.

294
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:54,480
Everyone changes a little
when they find out about it.

295
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:58,079
