or start hating me.

296
00:22:59,619 --> 00:23:02,390
Anyway, I guess things can't be
the same as before.

297
00:23:02,990 --> 00:23:04,250
It's not like that.

298
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:07,319
But there's one person...

299
00:23:08,660 --> 00:23:11,259
who hasn't changed at all around me.

300
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:14,769
Is it Ro Woon?

301
00:23:14,869 --> 00:23:15,970
Right.

302
00:23:17,730 --> 00:23:21,140
Her belittling attitude toward me
does annoy me a bit, though.

303
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:27,410
- Thanks for this.
- Don't mention it.

304
00:23:32,250 --> 00:23:34,380
By the way, can I ask you something?

305
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:39,519
Why did Mr. Kang go back already?

306
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:46,599
Okay, fine. I'll keep my mouth shut.

307
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:50,299
- By any chance...
- The red light is on.

308
00:23:50,769 --> 00:23:52,670
You're defeating the purpose
of the signal light.

309
00:23:54,099 --> 00:23:57,170
