313
00:24:08,390 --> 00:24:10,990
Are you extra sensitive today
because you couldn't get any sleep?

314
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:13,220
Was my snoring that bad?

315
00:24:13,890 --> 00:24:16,529
Enough to make both of you
run out of the room?

316
00:24:16,630 --> 00:24:19,529
Is that also why Mr. Kang
went back to Seoul early...

317
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:23,369
Come on.
That's not what happened, right?

318
00:24:23,630 --> 00:24:25,470
It mustn't have been that bad.

319
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:29,970
By the way, that flower
really suits you. Do you know that?

320
00:24:40,119 --> 00:24:41,250
I want to go back.

321
00:24:41,279 --> 00:24:42,589
- Shall we go back?
- Really?

322
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:44,789
(Welcome, Yun Jung.)

323
00:24:46,259 --> 00:24:50,359
(Welcome, Yun Jung.)

324
00:24:50,529 --> 00:24:52,759
(10 years ago)

325
00:24:54,059 --> 00:24:55,069
(Welcome, Yun Jung.)

326
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:01,269
(Welcome, Yun Jung.)

327
00:25:12,420 --> 00:25:15,420
(Welcome, Yun Jung.)

328
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:35,710
Hwan Gi.

329
00:25:37,609 --> 00:25:40,839
When did you start
wearing that hoodie?

330
00:25:41,579 --> 00:25:42,579
Oh, this.

331
00:25:44,009 --> 00:25:45,150
When I was in college.

332
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:47,079
Why? Did something happen?

333
00:25:48,180 --> 00:25:49,819
Was it because of a girl?

334
00:25:50,589 --> 00:25:52,220
A heartbreak from your first love?

335
00:25:53,390 --> 00:25:54,990
Gosh, that must've been
what happened.

336
00:25:55,390 --> 00:25:56,890
What was she like?

337
00:25:57,430 --> 00:25:59,799
Any tear-invoking stories
you want to share?

338
00:26:00,259 --> 00:26:01,259
Tell me.

339
00:26:02,069 --> 00:26:03,329
It's none of your business.

340
00:26:07,869 --> 00:26:09,269
I think it's him.

341
00:26:12,339 --> 00:26:13,339
Hello.

342
00:26:14,839 --> 00:26:17,250
(New York Barbershop)

343
00:26:34,500 --> 00:26:37,130
