like his daughter is back yet.

344
00:26:37,599 --> 00:26:39,039
She didn't even leave a note.

345
00:26:39,069 --> 00:26:41,839
How many days has it been
since she just took off?

346
00:26:59,089 --> 00:27:00,160
Goodness.

347
00:27:09,730 --> 00:27:11,799
He must be so worried.

348
00:27:18,880 --> 00:27:21,109
- There she is. She's back!
- What?

349
00:27:21,710 --> 00:27:23,109
Yes, she's back.

350
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:32,259
I guess we'll get
to hear him yelling this time.

351
00:27:32,319 --> 00:27:34,190
He's been too lenient with her.

352
00:27:34,220 --> 00:27:36,789
He really should
teach her a lesson this time.

353
00:27:36,859 --> 00:27:37,930
Absolutely.

354
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:40,829
Yes! Good. Way to go.

355
00:27:41,029 --> 00:27:43,869
Be a man.
Show her how scary you can be!

356
00:27:48,710 --> 00:27:49,839
Have you eaten yet?

357
00:27:55,650 --> 00:27:57,809
Yes, I have.

358
00:28:02,349 --> 00:28:03,349
What did he say?

359
00:28:04,150 --> 00:28:05,289
He asked her if she's eaten.

360
00:28:18,299 --> 00:28:19,569
I've eaten as well.

361
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:28,009
You remind me
of someone I used to know...

362
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,579
even though you two
aren't really similar.

363
00:28:44,460 --> 00:28:45,559
Yes, Mr. Park.

364
00:28:47,730 --> 00:28:51,500
(New Year Message
for the Brain Family)

365
00:28:51,529 --> 00:28:54,140
(Mr. Kang Woo Il and my daughter
are getting married.)

366
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:56,009
He's getting married.

367
00:28:56,069 --> 00:28:57,910
He wasn't going to be mine anyway.

368
00:28:58,009 --> 00:28:59,710
But this is so sudden.

369
00:29:01,079 --> 00:29:02,680
I can't believe it.

370
00:29:02,779 --> 00:29:05,819
The founder of Brain wrote
this message himself...

371
00:29:05,880 --> 00:29:08,720
for all of the employees.
It's obviously not some gibberish.

372
00:29:12,619 --> 00:29:14,920
So he announced it like this.

373
00:29:15,789 --> 00:29:17,890
I thought you were aware of it.

374
00:29:19,599 --> 00:29:20,829
Mr. Kang.

375
00:29:24,029 --> 00:29:25,640
Congratulations on your engagement.

376
00:29:26,299 --> 00:29:27,640
Congratulations.

377
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:31,509
- Mr. Kang, congratulations.
- Congratulations.

378
00:29:31,539 --> 00:29:33,109
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

379
00:29:33,140 --> 00:29:34,480
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

380
00:29:37,349 --> 00:29:38,519
You're here.

381
00:29:47,119 --> 00:29:49,630
You announced my engagement.

382
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:53,200
I went out of my way
to make you proud.

383
00:29:54,799 --> 00:29:56,700
You didn't say anything to me.

384
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:59,039
And I was away.

385
00:29:59,069 --> 00:30:01,269
- You can leave now.
- Okay.

386
00:30:03,809 --> 00:30:06,710
I've been a little cold to you
lately.

387
00:30:07,039 --> 00:30:08,910
It's not because I hate you.

388
00:30:09,410 --> 00:30:11,980
It's because I trust you.
I feel comfortable around you.

389
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:14,849
I rely on you
more than I do to my own son.

390
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:20,460
My son achieved an okay result
this time,

391
00:30:20,690 --> 00:30:22,990
but he still has a long way to go.

392
00:30:24,029 --> 00:30:26,630
Please help him come to the front...

393
00:30:27,299 --> 00:30:28,930
and lead the company.

394
00:30:29,329 --> 00:30:33,200
You've been carrying
so much burden by yourself.

395
00:30:33,799 --> 00:30:34,869
Am I wrong?

396
00:30:35,910 --> 00:30:38,039
You want Hwan Gi to stand out...

397
00:30:39,839 --> 00:30:41,140
more than I do, right?

398
00:30:41,339 --> 00:30:44,450
I just slapped you in the face once.

399
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,079
Are you still holding a grudge?

400
00:30:46,579 --> 00:30:47,720
I wish...

401
00:30:48,589 --> 00:30:51,019
you were my son...

402
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:53,319
a dozen times a day.

403
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:56,430
I'm even giving my daughter to you.

404
00:30:56,529 --> 00:30:59,630
- Father, I appreciate that, but...
- Still,

405
00:31:00,130 --> 00:31:02,369
don't get too excited
about your wedding.

406
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:05,900
Don't neglect the election
or the company.

407
00:31:06,569 --> 00:31:10,569
We still don't know who released the
article on Hwan Gi's power abuse.

408
00:31:17,609 --> 00:31:18,819
Woo Il.

409
00:31:21,279 --> 00:31:22,619
You were surprised, right?

410
00:31:22,849 --> 00:31:26,319
Mom was worried you were not
interested in marrying me.

411
00:31:26,589 --> 00:31:29,390
She was making a fuss
saying she has a bad feeling.

412
00:31:29,829 --> 00:31:32,529
While trying to defend you,
things got out of hand.

413
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:35,160
- I'm sorry, but...
- That's what I want to say.

414
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:40,500
I can't postpone our wedding
any longer than this.

415
00:31:40,740 --> 00:31:42,009
Yi Soo.

416
00:31:45,309 --> 00:31:46,779
Stay with me.

417
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:49,180
That's the only thing...

418
00:31:51,579 --> 00:31:52,950
I ask of you.

419
00:31:59,559 --> 00:32:01,190
He caught me off guard.

420
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:04,029
I knew how controlling he can be,
but I didn't expect this.

421
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:07,930
Ro Woon is giving me
enough headaches.

422
00:32:09,230 --> 00:32:10,869
Now, a wedding announcement?

423
00:32:14,369 --> 00:32:15,710
Let's fire Ro Woon.

424
00:32:17,339 --> 00:32:19,079
That'll be best for her too.

425
00:32:20,609 --> 00:32:23,509
- Let's not take any action...
- We should have earlier.

426
00:32:23,650 --> 00:32:26,049
If she's planning something
in addition to that article...

427
00:32:26,079 --> 00:32:27,680
She won't do anything more.

428
00:32:29,390 --> 00:32:31,250
Then why is she still here?

429
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:33,789
She must be trying to dig into
what happened three years ago.

430
00:32:35,089 --> 00:32:36,960
If she finds out...

431
00:32:39,630 --> 00:32:41,400
Is that what you're going for?

432
00:32:42,730 --> 00:32:45,130
That's my biggest weakness.
Is that why you...

433
00:32:45,170 --> 00:32:47,240
- Are you saying I'm...
- Then?

434
00:32:48,269 --> 00:32:49,710
You said you want to protect her.
Why are you keeping her here?

435
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:51,170
It just doesn't make sense.

436
00:32:53,609 --> 00:32:55,180
Give me some time.

437
00:32:57,250 --> 00:32:58,380
Why?

438
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:02,019
What are you thinking about
all alone now?

439
00:33:03,349 --> 00:33:06,289
It's me. You can talk to me.

440
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:10,589
Wasn't keeping her identity from me
all this time enough?

441
00:33:20,970 --> 00:33:22,569
Only my secrets are found by you.

442
00:33:23,509 --> 00:33:26,180
You see through me.
Why can't I see who you are?

443
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:30,579
Can't I know what's on your mind?

444
00:33:42,730 --> 00:33:45,660
Yoo Hee wants Boss.

445
00:33:46,130 --> 00:33:47,829
She's starting a meeting.

446
00:33:48,460 --> 00:33:50,970
- It was a mistake.
- A mistake?

447
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:53,140
You know guys can make a mistake.

448
00:33:54,369 --> 00:33:56,670
What's going on between...

449
00:34:09,289 --> 00:34:10,420
Mr. Kang.

450
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:21,159
Boss, did something happen?

451
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:30,710
The war has begun.

452
00:34:30,869 --> 00:34:32,079
What do you mean?

453
00:34:32,210 --> 00:34:34,679
Mr. Kang's wedding
has been announced.

454
00:34:34,809 --> 00:34:37,079
He's going to be
the founder's son-in-law.

455
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:39,920
The son and the son-in-law will
fight over the management rights.

456
00:34:40,380 --> 00:34:42,250
This is the beginning
of that cruel battle.

457
00:34:42,289 --> 00:34:43,789
Here you go.

458
00:34:44,119 --> 00:34:46,420
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

459
00:34:46,889 --> 00:34:48,260
It's hot.

460
00:34:49,789 --> 00:34:51,090
It tastes good.

461
00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:56,929
I don't believe they argued
over such a thing.

462
00:34:56,969 --> 00:34:59,139
You never know.

463
00:34:59,599 --> 00:35:02,139
My mom fights with her sisters
all the time too.

464
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:05,239
- That's the way it is.
- Is this battle even possible?

465
00:35:09,949 --> 00:35:11,510
Exactly.

466
00:35:11,949 --> 00:35:14,219
Mr. Kang has shown so much so far.

467
00:35:14,949 --> 00:35:17,920
Mr. Eun doesn't have resources.

468
00:35:18,449 --> 00:35:20,389
- I feel sorry for him.
- So do I.

469
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:23,230
What could Mr. Eun do
without Mr. Kang?

470
00:35:24,329 --> 00:35:26,030
Sun Bong, come over here, will you?

471
00:35:26,130 --> 00:35:29,869
No. We better decide our positions
carefully now.

472
00:35:36,210 --> 00:35:38,070
- Bye.
- Wait.

473
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:41,280
Sun Bong, where are you going?

474
00:35:41,679 --> 00:35:43,250
We should help him.

475
00:35:48,449 --> 00:35:50,550
This is an old, small theater.

476
00:35:50,889 --> 00:35:54,219
